<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ez Channeling</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            line-height: 1.6;
            background: url('doctor8.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed; 
            background-size: cover; /* Full background image */
            color: white; /* Default text color */
        }

        header {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); /* Black header with transparency */
        }

        header h1 {
            color: #ffffff; /* White text */
        }

        .nav-link {
            color: #ffffff; /* White links */
        }

        #hero {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); /* Black section with transparency */
            padding: 50px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: #000; /* Black button */
            color: #ffffff; /* White text */
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #ffffff; /* White hover */
            color: #000; /* Black text on hover */
        }

        section {
            padding: 50px 0;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); /* Transparent black for sections */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Spacing between sections */
            border-radius: 5px; /* Rounded corners */
        }

        footer {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); /* Black footer with transparency */
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .list-group-item {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Transparent black for list items */
            border: none; /* Remove border */
            color: white; /* Text color */
        }

        .list-group-item:hover {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); /* Darker on hover */
        }

        .card {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Transparent black for cards */
            border: none; /* Remove border */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Spacing between cards */
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem; /* Increase card title size */
        }

        .fa {
            font-size: 2rem; /* Icon size */
            margin-bottom: 15px; /* Spacing below icon */
            color: #ff5733; /* Icon color */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="text-center py-4">
        <h1>Ez Channeling</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul class="nav justify-content-center">
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#services">Services</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#about">About Us</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="container my-5">
        <section id="hero" class="text-center">
            <h2>Book Your Appointment Online</h2>
            <p>Convenient and fast e-channeling service.</p>
            <a href="sample1.jsp" class="btn" >Book Now</a>
        </section>

        <section id="services" class="py-5">
            <h2 class="text-center">Our Services</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card text-center">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-md"></i>
                            <h5 class="card-title">Consultation</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Get professional advice from qualified doctors.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card text-center">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <i class="fas fa-history"></i>
                            <h5 class="card-title">Follow-up Appointments</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Schedule your follow-ups easily.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card text-center">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <i class="fas fa-laptop-medical"></i>
                            <h5 class="card-title">Virtual Health Checks</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Experience remote health checks from home.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="about" class="py-5">
            <h2 class="text-center">About Us</h2>
            <p class="text-center">At Ez Channeling, we aim to simplify healthcare access for everyone. Our platform allows patients to easily connect with qualified doctors and schedule appointments from the comfort of their homes. With a focus on convenience and safety, we provide a seamless experience that prioritizes your health and well-being. Our goal is to make healthcare more accessible and efficient for all.

</p>
        </section>

        <section id="contact" class="py-5">
            <h2 class="text-center">Contact Us</h2>
            <div class="text-center">
                <h5>Address:</h5>
                <p>eChannelling PLC, No: 108, W A D Ramanayake Mawatha, Colombo 2, Sri Lanka.</p>
                <h5>Email:</h5>
                <p>info@echannelling.com</p>
                <h5>Phone:</h5>
                <p>+94 71 0 225 225</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Ez Channeling. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
